videos.headline: Penguins played their best in Game 5 win
videos.description: Barry Melrose and Steve Levy explain how the Penguins were able to turn in their best game of the Stanley Cup Final with a 6-0 victory over the Predators.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Penguins played their best in Game 5 win) 2017/06/08 SC

videos.headline: Crosby: Subban was doing 'UFC move on my foot'
videos.description: Sidney Crosby explains what happened when he and P.K. Subban got into an altercation. Subban explains that if a situation like this arises again, he will leave it to the officials.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Crosby: Subban was doing 'UFC move on my foot') 2017/06/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Crosby: 'Turned the page' on the series
videos.description: Sidney Crosby explains how the Penguins were able to dominate the Predators in Game 5 and what the team needs to do in order to close out the series in Nashville.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Crosby: 'Turned the page' on the series) 2017/06/08
